This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as named entity recognition and normalization. The use of deep neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the focus on medical literature datasets suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
